{"word":"H7219 - רֹאשׁ - rôʼsh - roshe - Gall","slug":"H7219","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רֹאשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>rôʼsh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>roshe"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gall"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D5;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E8;&#x05D0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1; - ro&#x0302;'sh  ro&#x0302;sh</b> - <i>roshe, roshe</i><p/>Apparently the same as <a href=\"#/H7218\">H7218</a>; a poisonous <i>plant</i>, probably the <i>poppy</i> (from its conspicuous <i>head</i>); generally <i>poison</i> (even of serpents): - gall, hemlock, posion, venom."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4761\">H4761</a>, <a href=\"#/H4763\">H4763</a>, <a href=\"#/H7218\">H7218</a>, <a href=\"#/H7220\">H7220</a>, <a href=\"#/H7221\">H7221</a>, <a href=\"#/H7222\">H7222</a>, <a href=\"#/H7223\">H7223</a>, <a href=\"#/H7224\">H7224</a>, <a href=\"#/H7225\">H7225</a>, <a href=\"#/H7226\">H7226</a>"}]}